Package: ramen
Title: Reconstruction and Alignment of Microbial Exchange Networks
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person("Adrian", "Hirt", , "am.hirt@pm.me", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-1929-6629"))
Description: Reconstructs metabolic exchange networks from microbial community
    data and aligns them using functional overlap scores to quantify the
    similarity and dissimilarity of consortium-level metabolic function.
    Provides tools for visualization and comparison of microbial consortia
    from a network perspective.
